response.overview: Tommy Cruise really looks like the movie superstar, don't you think? Add a lot of friskiness, sensuality, a certain toughness, a sexy muscular body and two plush pillows you can call the ultimate ass, Tommy is a real turn-on. Mark Mason, super masculine, super dominant, super muscular, is a lot bigger than Tommy. So this match ends up being a little like David going up against a Goliath. If your thing is to see a very muscular all-male man dominating, with lots of wrestling holds and sheer muscle strength, another masculine smaller, younger, well-built guy, then this match is right up your alley. Mason folds, stretches, crushes and bends poor Cruise. He gets Tommy to say, "I give", and "mercy", quite a lot. Note that Cruise is quite articulate and has an understated sense of humor. His demeanor is sorely tried towards the end of the match when his face takes on a certain worry and panic. You simply cannot take your eyes off that beautiful, expressive face! And when he smiles - WOW!
response.title: High Stakes Wrestling 11
